#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:11
msgid "KGeography"
msgstr "KGeography"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:12
msgid "Geography learning tool"
msgstr "Una ferramienta pa deprender xeografía"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"KGeography is a geography learning tool, which allows you to learn about the "
"political divisions of some countries (divisions, capitals of those "
"divisions and their associated flags if there are some)."
msgstr ""
"KGeography ye una ferramienta pa deprender xeografía que te permite "
"deprender les divisiones polítiques de dalgunos países (divisiones, "
"capitales d'estes divisiones y les sos banderes asociaes si les hubiere)"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:15
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Funciones:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:17
msgid ""
"Browse the maps clicking in a map division to see its name, capital and flag"
msgstr ""
"Restola los mapes calcando nuna división del mapa pa ver la bandera, el nome "
"y la bandera de so"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:18
msgid "The game tells you a map division name and you have to click on it"
msgstr ""
"El xuegu amuesa'l nome d'una división nel mapa y tienes de calcar nella"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:19
msgid ""
"The game tells you a capital and you have to guess the division it belongs to"
msgstr ""
"El xuegu amuesa una capital y tienes d'aldovinar la división a la que "
"pertenez"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:20
msgid "The game tells you a division and you have to guess its capital"
msgstr "El xuegu amuesa una división y tienes d'aldovinar la so capital"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:21
msgid "The game shows you a map division flag and you have to guess its name"
msgstr ""
"El xuegu amuesa la bandera d'una división nel mapa y tienes d'aldovinar el "
"so nome"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:22
msgid "The game tells you a map division name and you have to guess its flag"
msgstr ""
"El xuegu amuesa'l nome d'una división nel mapa y tienes d'aldovinar la so "
"bandera"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgeography.appdata.xml:23
msgid ""
"The game shows an empty map and you have to place divisions on it one by one"
msgstr ""
"El xuegu amuesa un mapa baleru y tienes d'asitiar les divisiones una a una"

